 -- Jordi Mallach <jordi@debian.org>  Fri, 06 Aug 2021 01:02:47 +0200

mailutils (1:3.11.1-5) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Enable PostgreSQL support now that OpenSSL is considered a system
    library by Debian ftpmaster.
  * Add upstream patch to fix expunging of mboxes on read-only directories
    (like Debian's /var/mail). Thanks to Pierrick Chanteux for the analysis
    (closes: #980042).
  * Add patch to fix PostgreSQL include dir.

 -- Jordi Mallach <jordi@debian.org>  Tue, 09 Feb 2021 16:17:12 +0100

mailutils (1:3.11.1-4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Pass -k to make check, so test failures don't halt the build, in
    order to detect additional failures later in the testsuite.
  * Add patch from Rob Browning to switch to guile-3.0 (closes: #969675).
  * Add additional upstream patches to fix testsuite failures.
  * Upload to unstable.

